---
---
<section class="swamp-utility" id="utility">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="utility-header">
      <h2 class="text-gradient">SWAMP POWER</h2>
      <p>More than just a meme. Features with layers.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="utility-grid">
      <!-- Item 1 -->
      <div class="utility-card glass-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🧅</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>ONION STAKING</h3>
          <p>Compound your $SHREK simply by holding. The deeper you go, the more layers of rewards you unlock.</p>
          <div class="status-tag">ACTIVE</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 2 -->
      <div class="utility-card glass-card">
        <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>SWAMP-FAST</h3>
          <p>Solana-powered speed. Instant transactions with near-zero gas for ultra-low latency rewards.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 3 -->
      <div class="utility-card glass-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🛡️</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>OGRE SECURITY</h3>
          <p>Audit-ready code and locked liquidity. Your swamp is protected by disciplined security measures.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 4 -->
      <div class="utility-card glass-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🗳️</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>GOVERNANCE</h3>
          <p>Decentralized decision making. The community decides the future of the swamp evolution.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .swamp-utility {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: #000;
  }

  .utility-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .utility-header h2 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
  .utility-header p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 1rem; }

  .utility-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .utility-card {
    position: relative;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 220px;
    background: var(--glass);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .utility-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(164, 198, 57, 0.1);
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .card-body h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .card-body p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .status-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--primary);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .utility-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .utility-card { min-height: auto; padding: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
